      "rationale": "Primary QoI is the normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) and relative hemolysis index (RH). These are directly mapped to the COU acceptance criterion RH < 1. Secondary QoIs include shear stress scalar distribution and exposure time histogram, which are inputs to the power-law hemolysis model. Full traceability from model output to decision criterion established."
