      "rationale": "Reynolds-averaged Navier-Stokes with k-omega SST turbulence closure selected. Blood treated as Newtonian fluid (justified for shear rates > 100 s⁻¹ prevalent in CPB pump). Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) applied. Model form assumptions documented in simulation plan. Gradation 1 achieved."
